<h3>Summary&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>At this point, you should have a good understanding of the way business functions relate to the options and personalization choices you have when it comes to your major within Smeal. This lesson also should have provided you a good starting point for your majors &amp; careers project, which you will work with your team to complete before the end of the semester.&nbsp;
</p>
