<h3>Assignment&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>The other major project you will complete for this class is the Company Research project. Part of the company research project is tied to the Majors &amp; Careers project, so it is important to complete the company research project by the deadline so you have all the information you need to finish the Majors &amp; Careers project.&nbsp;
</p>
<p>For details on the Company Research project, see the assignment in Canvas. Please note, the Company Research assignment is an individual assignment, however, you should work with your group to decide who will research which companies associated with the major your group chose. After companies have been assigned to group members, the company research is to be done individually. Each group member should only research one company.&nbsp;
</p>
<p>Please assign your companies to each group member by next week's class. A business librarian will be presenting in class next week to go over how to use the library's databases, so it is appropriate to wait until after the presentation to formally begin if you would like.&nbsp;
</p>
